description: The point shapefile shows cities where Toyota dealerships received complaints about defective Prius cars. It also has information when available about the type of defect, count of injuries and deaths if any due to the defect. Look for a map based on this data on Maker! Look elsewhere on Finder! for defective car complaints against all Toyota models. key words: Toyota, "car complaints"
